ADDENDUM: See the end of \"Spectra of Random Matrices\" (Notebook: 6 February \
2010), where I record first encounter with the command\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.523969536546591*^9, 3.52396962095792*^9}, {
  3.523969661616404*^9, 3.523969676106531*^9}}],

